rows.label: bf08430100_0010
rows.name: You can't control it, can you?

rows.label: bf08430100_0020
rows.name:
So you've been made the Cardinal's assistant.
Congratulations.

rows.label: bf08430100_0040
rows.name: I just came to say goodbye.

rows.label: bf08430100_0050
rows.name:
You'd be in a tough spot 
if I vanished without warning.

rows.label: bf08430100_0060
rows.name:
Goodbye?
What do you intend to do by leaving me?

rows.label: bf08430100_0080
rows.name: I... can use all my power even alone.

rows.label: bf08430100_0085
rows.name: I'll keep existing even if [System:Ruby rt=You ]Driver[/System:Ruby] die.

rows.label: bf08430100_0100
rows.name:
The Holy See, believers... I despise them all. Humans
\a are waste for this world, but they still have use.

rows.label: bf08430100_0110
rows.name: I figured I'd help you achieve that desire of yours.

rows.label: bf08430100_0140
rows.name:
That's exactly why you sought the supreme being...
God, and climbed the World Tree.

rows.label: bf08430100_0170
rows.name:
Someone must exist out there
who can utilize this Core Crystal...

rows.label: bf08430100_0180
rows.name: I'll have that person handle Metsu...
